{{Top|leg}}
'''Dybersyne''' was a manufacturer of magnetic rings. Working with the [[EngSat Complex]], it began production on the largest focusing magnet ever built, which was to be used for the [[Death Star/Legends|Death Star's]] primary weapon.

{{Company-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The name 'Dybersyne' is almost certainly a play on 'Cyberdyne', the company in [[Wikipedia:Terminator series|''The Terminator'' movies]] that constructed the T-800 Terminator and the genocidal supercomputer Skynet.

